OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,FAn investigation into allegations
OL,7,Fagainst Guernsey Police's former Chief
OL,8,FOfficer, Ruari Hardy, has found he did
OL,9,Fnot provide false information to
OL,10,Fmislead the Royal Court.
OL,12,FIt comes after a complaint was made in
OL,13,FDecember 2023, alleging that Hardy
OL,14,Fknowingly provided false information
OL,15,Funder oath in an attempt to mislead
OL,16,Fthe Guernsey Royal Court as part of a
OL,17,Fcivil case.
