OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,F"My approach to the matter in question
OL,7,Fwas always based upon facts and
OL,8,Fdefendable decisions, with the safety
OL,9,Fof this island community at the
OL,10,Fforefront of my mind.
OL,12,F"Whilst the barrage of inappropriate
OL,13,Fand unfounded allegations from this
OL,14,Fcomplainant has been distressing for
OL,15,Fme personally, it has been just as
OL,16,Fupsetting for serving officers and
OL,17,Ftheir families to witness.
OL,19,F"I am very pleased that this has now
OL,20,Fbeen concluded and that my integrity
OL,21,Fwhilst in office has been upheld."
