OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,FMr Hardy retired last year, but this
OL,7,Fwas unrelated to the investigation.
OL,9,FA statement from The Committee for
OL,10,FHome Affairs reads: "Former CO Hardy
OL,11,Fserved Guernsey Police as a
OL,13,Fdedicated leader for nearly six years,
OL,14,Fand retired last year, concluding a
OL,15,Fcareer in which he gave excellent
OL,16,Fsupport and leadership to the
OL,17,FBailiwick community.
